public interface MergeFlow
extends SingleSuccessorFlow, JoinFlow

A JoinFlow which merges several incoming branches into a single outgoing branch. A class implementing this interface must handle the incoming branches in an internal structure and must also manage separately each Element.

Yeray Callero
